  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We have always believed that God sent his son into the world to save us. But, what if that is not what happened? What if the world cannot be saved? <strong>The real story is about to be revealed</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DESOLATIUM: PROLOGUE</strong> is a first-person point & click Graphic Adventure based on Lovecraft Mythos. Live this horror story where you will have to visit mysterious locations, face lovecraftian creatures, find clues and combine objects to solve puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE MYSTERIOUS LOCATIONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a city outside the limits of time and space; meet mysterious characters who will guide you on your journey. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640540/extras/2308ab5c2006b5e77ace2f4055a6e7b1.poster.avif?t=1751535740\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640540/extras/2308ab5c2006b5e77ace2f4055a6e7b1.webm?t=1751535740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640540/extras/2308ab5c2006b5e77ace2f4055a6e7b1.mp4?t=1751535740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FACE LOVECRAFTIAN CREATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face lovecraftian creatures that came from the most remote places in the universe to test your sanity. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640540/extras/49bb4d0b29e391f96bde305cd5b7a3ce.poster.avif?t=1751535740\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640540/extras/49bb4d0b29e391f96bde305cd5b7a3ce.webm?t=1751535740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640540/extras/49bb4d0b29e391f96bde305cd5b7a3ce.mp4?t=1751535740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIND CLUES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find clues to move forward and uncover an intriguin backstory. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640540/extras/3d1c69ed25479ca1680f755711b3e02d.poster.avif?t=1751535740\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640540/extras/3d1c69ed25479ca1680f755711b3e02d.webm?t=1751535740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640540/extras/3d1c69ed25479ca1680f755711b3e02d.mp4?t=1751535740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COMBINE OBJECTS TO SOLVE PUZZLES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with the objects around you to solve complex puzzles in order to get to the terrible presence of a cosmic entity of immense power: Cthulhu. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640540/extras/ac3359c4b29b3915f8de4d5952793125.poster.avif?t=1751535740\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640540/extras/ac3359c4b29b3915f8de4d5952793125.webm?t=1751535740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640540/extras/ac3359c4b29b3915f8de4d5952793125.mp4?t=1751535740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We have always believed that God sent his son into the world to save us. But, what if that is not what happened? What if the world cannot be saved? <strong>The real story is about to be revealed</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DESOLATIUM: PROLOGUE</strong> is a first-person point & click Graphic Adventure based on Lovecraft Mythos. Live this horror story where you will have to visit mysterious locations, face lovecraftian creatures, find clues and combine objects to solve puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE MYSTERIOUS LOCATIONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a city outside the limits of time and space; meet mysterious characters who will guide you on your journey. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640540/extras/2308ab5c2006b5e77ace2f4055a6e7b1.poster.avif?t=1751535740\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640540/extras/2308ab5c2006b5e77ace2f4055a6e7b1.webm?t=1751535740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640540/extras/2308ab5c2006b5e77ace2f4055a6e7b1.mp4?t=1751535740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FACE LOVECRAFTIAN CREATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face lovecraftian creatures that came from the most remote places in the universe to test your sanity. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640540/extras/49bb4d0b29e391f96bde305cd5b7a3ce.poster.avif?t=1751535740\" width=600 height=20